HEADWORD: Osmaterium
<hw>Os`ma*te"ri*um</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Osmateria</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[NL.,
fr. Gr. <?/ smell.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>One of a pair of scent
organs which the larvae of certain butterflies emit from the first body
